CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 21, 1946, pg. 8 reads: "Pretty Wedding Party - Pictured following their recent marriage are the newlyweds, Mr. and Mrs. Charles Henry Robinson, surrounded by their wedding party. Left to right: Bernice Swann, Earl Johnson, Ardeth Swann, best man John Owens, the newlyweds, maid of honor Jean Swann, R.R. Swann and Frances Swann.  The bride is the former Dorothy Swann Edwards, daughter of Mrs. Veryle Swann Edwards. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Charles Henry Robinson and Dorothy Swann Edwards Robinson, posed in domestic interior with landscape vignette wallpaper
